Build instructions:
  unpack annoyance-filter--1.0d-1-src.tar.bz2
    if you use setup to install this src package, it will be
    unpacked under /usr/src automatically
  cd /usr/src
  ./annoyance-filter*.sh all

This will create:
  annoyance-filter--1.0d-1.tar.bz2
  annoyance-filter--1.0d-1-src.tar.bz2

